founded on the two countries' foreign policies of mutual respect for
sovereignty and territorial integrity, equality and peaceful
co-existence," he said.
</P>
<P>
He described China as "an all weather friend to Zambia", saying
that the Zambian government and people are happily looking forward to
the visit by Li Peng and believe that the visit will strengthen
further the friend bilateral relationship. enditem

