<HEADLINE> Shanghai Witnesses Increases of Technological Exports </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, May 1 (Xinhua) -- Shanghai's technology exports of
have been surged since the beginning of this year.
</P>
<P>
The change in the structure of technological exports is one
reason why many overseas businessmen have placed their confidence
in Shanghai technology, local officials said.
</P>
<P>
Previously, Shanghai's technological exports had been confined
mainly to traditional technologies and practical skills. Over the
past years, the export of high and new technologies have made up a
larger proportion of the total exports.
</P>
<P>
The number of agencies engaged in exports of high and new
technologies in the city has increased from 300 to 350, which are
exporting 300 items of high and new technologies.
</P>
<P>
In addition to sponsoring and holding technological fairs
overseas, Shanghai has also cooperated closely with foreign firms
by jointly operating high and new technological businesses in
Shanghai, so as to increase availability of locally-produced
technological products on the overseas market with the aid of the
overseas partners. This method of exporting accounted for 70
percent of technological exports to Europe and America, said local
officials.
</P>
<P>
According to local sources, the city earned over 500 million
U.S. dollars from technological exports last year. 
</P>
</TEXT>
