<HEADLINE> South China Increasing Help for Laid-off Workers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HAIKOU, May 1 (Xinhua) -- South China's Hainan Province is
stepping up its efforts to help laid-off workers find new jobs.
</P>
<P>
