This capital city of the province holds forums twice a month
for redundant workers to help them find new jobs.
</P>
<P>
Relevant figures show that the province spent approximately
three million yuan (about 375,000 US dollars) in 1996 to run
various kinds of technical training classes to help redundant
workers, who now number about 50,000, to find new jobs.  
