<TEXT>
<P>
TEGUCIGALPA, April 30 (Xinhua) -- Honduras and Nicaragua agreed
today to exchange the fishermen detained by their respective
countries, Nicaragua's Ambassador to Honduras Manuel Rivas
Gasteazoro said here.
</P>
<P>
